notesStmt.note: Much damaged. Folios stuck on paper.
Only part of folio 4 is preserved.
Manuscript description based on Margoliouth, G.: Catalogue of the Hebrew and Samaritan Manuscripts in the British Museum, London 1965.

msContents.summary: Several fragments of Judeo-Arabic commentaries on the Pentateuch.
